name: Warung Babi Guling Putra Celagi
address: Jl. Desa Apuan No.87, Apuan, Kec. Susut, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80661, Indonesia
review 1: The food is nice despite having some of it are hard (hard to digest). The place itself is nice and has kid friendly meal.
review 2: The Best Babi Guling in Gianyar Area so Far. But its located in Bangli Regency. Worth to try, Cheap. 70.000 rupiah for two. Dont left Bali before you try Babi Guling especially this one
review 3: Nasi Campur ok,too bad  we missed  Pork Skin ,next time make sure you order pork skin  in advance
review 4: The best babi guling in town. Only Rp. 20.000 per plate for a complete package. Skip the blood sausage and get extra pork rind. Come in the morning otherwise you will miss the skin. Finish your meal by stopping at Kalantala Street for dessert: klepon--gloutenous rice moci filled with palm sugar and topped with coconut.
review 5:
Hidden gem in rural area of Klungkung. Delicious food with variety of drinks including local beers. Green scenery and awesome service are bonus!

IDR 25 k for a meal

Cons: no parking area and road is quite narrow
